    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for daily transportation. While it shows clear signs of its age and mileage, including some minor cosmetic blemishes on the exterior and visible wear on the interior upholstery, the engine and transmission remain functional. You can expect a reliable drive from point A to point B, though it may require some upcoming routine maintenance to keep it in peak operating form. It's a solid choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly, functional car without the premium price tag of a newer model.",
