    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride? I'm selling my car and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it runs like a dream. It has a few little signs of love here and there, but nothing that takes away from how great it looks on the road. It\u2019s perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home where it'll be appreciated. Come by, check it out, and let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted driver's car featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six paired with a desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The double VANOS system has been overhauled, and the rod bearings were replaced as preventative maintenance. Crucially, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to maintain structural integrity under load. The chassis benefits from a limited-slip differential and a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein dampers for exceptional lateral grip and feedback. While the exterior shows light, honest wear, the drivetrain and powertrain remain in peak operational form, making this an ideal specimen for the purist who prioritizes performance and mechanical longevity.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
