    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and care, making it an ideal choice for a buyer who appreciates mechanical soundess and a clean aesthetic. The exterior paint retains a beautiful luster, though a discerning eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a light surface scratch near the fuel door\u2014small imperfections that do not detract from its striking presence. Inside, the cabin has been kept in excellent order; the upholstery is free of tears or stains, and the dashboard remains crack-free with all original buttons and switches fully operational. Under the hood, the car has been maintained with precision. It features a complete service log, including a recent cooling system flush and a brand-new set of performance tires. The engine idles smoothly and delivers power effortlessly, while the suspension remains tight and responsive over varied road surfaces. This is a turn-key vehicle that has been loved by its previous owner and is ready for its next chapter with no immediate service needs.",
      "price": 36800.0,
